{"type":"message","id":"d30889c3","parentId":"d70fdac3","timestamp":"2026-03-20T00:50:16.338Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Context usage is at 20%, which is well below the threshold. Everything is fine. The system is operating normally.","thinkingSignature":"94d6a2280cadf6de50c4d9d31b8ca62b5b9d66f3b226998363577d10f1616b42"},{"type":"text","text":"📊 **Context Monitor Report**\n\n**时间:** 2026-03-20 08:50 (Asia/Shanghai)\n\n| 指标 | 数值 |\n|------|------|\n| Context 使用 | 20% (40,887 / 200,000 tokens) |\n| 状态 | ✅ 正常 |\n\n一切正常，context 充足，无需操作。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":1322,"output":102,"cacheRead":37099,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":38523,"cost":{"input":0.0005288000000000001,"output":0.000153,"cacheRead":0.00148396,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00216576}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773967812761}}
